672	34	5	f	f	t	t	f	"[\\"User Control and Freedom\\",\\"Help Users Recognize, Diagnose, and Recover from Errors\\",\\"Recognition Rather than Recall\\",\\"Match between System and the Real World\\",\\"Help Users Recognize, Diagnose, and Recover from Errors\\",\\"Core Principles Summary\\\\n​1. Visual Elements\\\\n​These are the building blocks of any interface. They include typography, color, icons, and whitespace. Effective use of visual elements ensures that the interface is not only attractive but also functional. For example, using a consistent color for all clickable buttons helps users identify interactive parts of the screen.\\\\n​2. Information Hierarchy\\\\n​This is the arrangement of elements in a way that implies importance. By using size, contrast, and placement, you guide the user's eye to the most critical information first.\\\\n​Top-level: Main headings or \\\\\\"Call to Action\\\\\\" buttons.\\\\n​Secondary: Subheadings and supporting text.\\\\n​Tertiary: Metadata or footer links.\\\\n​3. Consistency\\\\n​Consistency ensures that the interface is predictable.\\\\n​Internal Consistency: Using the same styles for the same elements throughout the single app (e.g., all \\\\\\"Delete\\\\\\" buttons are red).\\\\n​External Consistency: Following industry standards so users don't have to relearn how to use your app (e.g., placing the logo in the top-left corner).\\\\n​4. Interface Readability\\\\n​Readability focuses on how easily a user can consume text and data. This involves:\\\\n​Contrast: High contrast between text and background.\\\\n​Line Length and Spacing: Ensuring text isn't too cramped or too wide.\\\\n​Legibility: Choosing fonts that are easy to read at various sizes.\\",\\"Warna yang berada tepat berseberangan dalam color wheel\\",\\"Typeface adalah keluarga desain huruf, font adalah kombinasi typeface, ukuran, dan gaya\\",\\" Karena jika karakter mudah dibedakan, keseluruhan teks lebih mudah dipahami\\",\\" Common Region\\",\\"Skala ruang kosong antara bagian besar dan elemen kecil\\",\\"Flowlines\\",\\"Single column grid\\",\\"Detail dan kompleks agar terlihat profesional\\"]"	40		2026-02-25 06:33:29.254	2026-03-01 13:25:00.861	0		2026-02-25 06:33:29.941	2026-03-01 13:25:01.484	"[]"
